          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-trigger">Do you offer support in languages other than English? <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-body"><p>Yes — we provide support in 18 languages including Arabic, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Mandarin, Hindi, Urdu, Swahili, and more. Just let our team know your preferred language.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-trigger">Where can I find my account number and sort code? <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-body"><p>These are found in the app under Account → Details. You can also find them on your monthly statement. If you've lost app access, call us to verify identity and we'll provide them.</p></div>
